{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "音樂室內的光芒", "storyInfo": "與前雇主的誤會一直如同陰霾困擾著海鈴，就在她苦惱是否加入老爺的家族時，被抓的祥子揭露了老爺的陰謀。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始，我只當作是接到了一份再普通不過的工作。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個沒沒無名的小家族需要我的力量，以便在風雨飄搖的敘拉古站穩腳跟。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而隨著日子一天天過去，他們越來越信任我，甚至帶我參加家族的核心會議。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明知這與合約內容不符，卻又很享受待在這些人中的感覺。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g10_smallrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲！海鈴小妹妹，好幾天不見了，你還好嗎？", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，橘子口味的奶凍。我沒記錯的話，你喜歡這個口味吧？", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，我自己有。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*哥倫比亞粗口*，不要這麼不領情啦！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是聽說你單槍匹馬把之前騷擾我們的那群傢伙趕走了，想感謝你一下啊！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離我遠一點。我只是個拿錢辦事的打手，做完這票就會離開。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果等一下你們老大看到我們兩個混在一起，你肯定沒有好下場。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係啦，老大上次跟我說了，他早就想邀請你加入我們了……", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我建議你們還是再多打聽一下我在敘拉古的名聲吧。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用打聽啦，你已經是我們見過的最強的人了！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，你不如現在就答應吧。今晚的家族聚餐，我們一起去啊——", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#12$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其說是家族聚餐，不如說是樂隊表演吧……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#12$3"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，我們家族的勢力雖然比較小，但成員之間的情誼是別人比不了的啊！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且你不是和我們一起表演了很多次嗎？大家都很有默契了啊。", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等我哪天有空再說吧。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你之前也是這樣說的——", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走了。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#1$3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g11_mansionhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拒絕了他的盛情邀約。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但回家的路上，我的心中卻湧起一種莫名的感覺。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種從未有過的感覺。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那晚我躺在床上輾轉反側，整夜未眠。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽還未升起之時，我就收拾好了所有的行李——"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#6$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……誰會找到這裡？", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#6$3"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，老爺那邊出了點狀況，想讓你幫忙頂罪。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我已經決定……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監獄那邊我們已經安排好了，他們正在下面等著。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是報酬，如果你覺得不夠，還可以再加。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，你今天怎麼回事？是我說錯什麼了嗎？", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前不是一直都是這樣嗎——我們出錢，你辦事。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快去吧，我們會想辦法幫你減到半年，半年就能出來了。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomC", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為被僱傭的打手，幫人頂罪是再正常不過的事，我對監獄的生活也再熟悉不過。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這次，唯獨這次，我卻無比地煎熬。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半年裡，我無時無刻不想著出獄，想回到那個家族中，回到他們的樂隊派對裡。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經決定好了自己的歸宿。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我沒想到，最後的結局卻是——"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainlight_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老大死了，大家都死了，幾百個人現在只剩我們十幾個了！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一群兄弟好不容易從哥倫比亞漂泊到這個鬼地方，結果全被你害死了！", "name": "弗朗西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這半年到底發生了什麼事情？"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，但我唯一知道的是——"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又一次失去了“家”。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g7_reception", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，你幫我做了這麼多件事，賣了這麼多次命，我應當給你一個身分。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我允許你加入我的家族。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#12$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你知道我從來都是獨來獨往，不會加入任何一個家族。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#12$3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#12$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不願，還是不能？", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，我和那些自稱“家族領袖”的地痞流氓不一樣。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這個地方和那些陰險狡詐的大家族鬥了大半輩子，從來沒有離開過牌桌。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你希望我幫你登上更大的牌桌？", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很聰明。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但和做交易不一樣，加入一個家族需要考慮的事情更多。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做交易只需考慮雇主的開價，加入一個家族則要考慮領袖的人品。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，我知道我的風評不算好，但這不就是我們相似的地方嗎？", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，除了我，還有人願意接納你嗎？", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敘拉古太危險，家族和秩序之下，全是陰謀和算計。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你上一次安穩地睡覺是什麼時候？", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "側躺在紙箱上，手中還要時時刻刻拿著匕首戒備……", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“獨狼終有歸宿”。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是回歸狼群，恢復身分和名譽……還是橫屍荒野，被野獸分食。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己選擇。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺，她引來了一些不乾淨的人。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "sw"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "sw"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 45.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子的雙手被反銬著，動彈不得。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一個傢伙跑了，我們正在派人追捕。", "name": "嚴肅的打手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_699_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，你認識這位小姐？", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不認識。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不記得我們的那些舊帳了？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看樣子是來尋仇的。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，我給你時間和場地，你自己處理。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過了，我不認識她……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#8$3"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你加入我的家族前的最後一項考驗。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次……就不要拿提前準備的血袋偽裝現場了。", "name": "蒼老的聲音"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.0, "x": 120.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "hr"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "hr", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordexsheath", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 120.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小巷裡，唯有祥子和海鈴兩個人。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她們知道，有人正在期待這場決鬥如何收場。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴知道，老爺正在看。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子知道，莫菲絲也在看。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟你無冤無仇，你何必尋死？", "name": "八幡海鈴"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是來接你回去的。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接我回去？", "name": "八幡海鈴"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是回撞球間，而是回到你本來應該在的地方。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽不懂你在說什麼。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算你聽不懂，我也必須拉住你，不能讓你就這樣去死。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗算弗朗西斯他們的人，就是老爺的手下。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不相信一個背地裡陷害你的人，會給你想要的歸宿。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……可是……", "name": "八幡海鈴"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無數次被人利用，無數次被當作棄子……這就是你想要的生活，這就是你想要的信任嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在這裡待了這麼久，甚至不願傷害任何一個人。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才在裡面的時候我看見了你的琴盒，裡面裝的是你的貝斯吧？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴，你本來不需要承受這種痛苦。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海鈴……和我一起離開吧。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "hr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}